{"tid":2304121,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG 箍牙集中討論區 34","createTime":"2020-11-28T13:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T06:17:36.000Z","uid":304990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"618cd766c80b78a9c2b95d7efff7e8384521187e","tid":2304121,"uid":304990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>箍牙Q&amp;A credit to 施華朗尼馬達巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎一齊集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：想箍牙，搵邊個好？<br />\nA：一般建議普通科牙醫或者牙齒矯正科專科。<br />\n名單呢到有：<a href=\"https://www.dchk.org.hk/tc/list/list.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dchk.org.hk%2Ftc%2Flist%2Flist.htm&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=9a3423bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dchk.org.hk/tc/list/list.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：普通科同專科有咩分別？<br />\nA：專科醫生成為普通牙醫後要進修多最少六年，可以處理複雜既牙齒問題，收費亦較貴。<br />\n<br />\nQ：箍牙一般有咩種類揀？<br />\nA：主要有傳統或者透明(隱適美)。<br />\n<br />\nQ：治療費大約幾多，包左D咩？<br />\nA：<br />\n普通科 - 傳統約$30000起，透明(隱適美)約$40000起<br />\n普通科收費一般已包括治療前X光片及牙模，箍牙費，一副固定器，箍牙所需之相關牙科費用(例如：剝牙、補牙、洗牙等)<br />\n專科 - 傳統約$40000起，透明(隱適美)約$50000起<br />\n專科收費一般只包括治療前X光片及牙模，箍牙費，一副固定器<br />\n**個別醫生收費會有不用，詳情請向診所查詢<br />\n<br />\nQ：想開始箍牙、療程係點？<br />\nA：首次諮詢(免費至過千元，部份會於治療費扣除) &gt; 制作矯齒記錄包括X光片、相片及牙模(一千至數千元，一般可以於治療費扣除) &gt; 醫生提供治療計劃(免費) &gt; 展開療程<br />\n<br />\nQ：廿幾歲先黎箍牙，會唔會太遲？<br />\nA：唔少人都係呢個歲數先箍<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩醫生、診所要小心？<br />\nA：康齒堂、網上遙距箍牙、淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n了解更多：20200406【杏林在線】傳統箍牙vs隱形牙套<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SY-WHgzNgyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSY-WHgzNgyo&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=9093b202\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SY-WHgzNgyo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bc469ecf98a53b3381852413571a64100dba3fb8","tid":2304121,"uid":304990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"諗住幫手開 原來有人已經開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家去翻嗰邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2300361\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2300361</a>"},{"pid":"f8a81f4ef31f4af20c46b633c1a2e40e5132ba7e","tid":2304121,"uid":348877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:17:36.000Z","msg":"cool左2年仲未cool完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}